_sText:
This is the first map ive made for CS:S i hope you like it. i have a server called "iNoob's Lair" if you want to come check it out thats where you'll find it ;)

i tried to do something that hasnt been done too much with fy maps. guns are dispersed thruout the levels. naturally you have to go further into the level to get the better guns, and you have to scale the entire map in order to be able to purchase anything... makes it more challenging.

features a bunker with a door on hinges, glass, ladders. its a pretty newb map but its pretty much done. id like some input on things to change/enhance. i dont know why the lighting is all wierd. everything seems to glow in neon for some reason. and you NEED to put "High Dynamic Range" on FULL to see this map properly...

you can find it in. options>video>advanced

anyways i await your input! -peace

-Elijah Lucian (aka iNoob)

p.s. it has a combine influence. kind of a futuristic clean but dirty kind of clash happening. i didnt know what to put on the theme so i put that...
